FBIS3-52194 "drnes001_s_94009" FBIS-NES-94-001 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Jan 1994 Iran Foreign Ministry Offers Aid on Kabul Fighting LD0101112294 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network in Persian 1030 GMT 1 Jan 94 LD0101112294 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran First Program Network Language: Persian Article Type:BFN [Text] In light of the fierce clashes taking place in Kabul since early today, the spokesman of our country's Foreign Ministry spoke to our correspondent, expressing deep regret at the occurrence of such clashes and calling on the warring sides to end the bloodshed as soon as possible and solve their problems peacefully. The Foreign Ministry spokesman announced the readiness of the Islamic Republic of Iran to help end the clashes.
